                     <interp inst="t18700404-342-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>, Stealing a horse and cart and set of harness, and 120 pounds of beef, of <persName id="t18700404-name-209" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18700404-name-209" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
